node.text:
Preorders | (What) did you order last Friday and when does it arrive (Or didn't you ordered anything yet).
⠀ 
As I heard and read, the ordering process boss quite a mess ... For Mia turned out well because are used to see Apple store app on the iPhone and everything went through seamlessly. 😬
⠀ 
I also had access a few minutes earlier than others that I talked to (who try to order via browser).
⠀ 
It seems that for a lot of customers the order process felt very unsatisfactory. Whether you ordered or not, feel free to leave your thoughts in the comments!
